title: Number of people freelancing in U.S. 2014 to 2019
yAxis: Number of people doing freelance work in million
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of people doing freelance work in million, containing a total of 6 data points.
Overall Number of people doing freelance work in million has increased over the Year.
Number of people doing freelance work in million is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2017, and finally roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Number of people doing freelance work in million, about 57.3 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Number of people doing freelance work in million about 53.0 was reached at Year 2014
